t of N.~Alrayes from\nthe square grid setting to the orthodiagonal setting, and prove that the\ndiscrete modulus of the approximating non-crossing paths converges to the\ncontinuous modulus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Jun 2021 21:35:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 22:52:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2022 14:11:47 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 5 Jun 2023 16:26:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-06"}
