lity, we achieved a data analysis rate which matches the data\nacquisition rate. Completing data analysis with 10 mins is a first for XFEL\nexperiments and an important milestone if we are to keep up with data\ncollection trends.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jun 2021 01:09:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 22:03:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-18"}
