rier height and\nexperimental measurement, and between the predictions from the FN DMC and G3\nmodel for the reaction energy provide a theoretical basis for resolving the\nenergy uncertainty in this reaction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jun 2021 14:37:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-23"}
