ts. In general, the optimisation and\nsimulation models differ in their respective strengths, justifying the\nexistence of both. While methods were generally rated as quite well developed,\ncombinatorial optimisation approaches, as well as machine learning, are\nidentified as important research methods to be developed further for ESA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jun 2021 09:23:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-28"}
